aim_manylanes

This is a small aim map.
At the beginning of the round, you got a deagle with 999 ammo and a knife.
There are many lanes, where you can go through.

In some of the lanes are smokegrenades or flashbangs!

I hope you have fun!
_____________________________________________________________________________________
